every_county = { 
	limit = { 
		is_valid_prov = yes
	}
	clear_variable_list = trade_dat_food
	clear_variable_list = array_trade_dat_food
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_dat_trade_in_food
		value = var:trade_in_food
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_dat_trade_out_food
		value = var:trade_out_food
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_dat_trade_earn_food
		value = var:trade_earn_food
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_dat_trade_pay_food
		value = var:trade_pay_food
	}
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_sply_$good$
			has_variable = trade_dmnd_$good$
			var:trade_sply_$good$ > 0
			var:trade_dmnd_$good$ > 0
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				var:trade_sply_$good$ = { 
					compare_value >= prev.var:trade_dmnd_$good$
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				name = trade_in_$good$
				value = var:trade_dmnd_$good$
			}
			set_variable = { 
				name = trade_out_$good$
				value = var:trade_dmnd_$good$
			}
		}
		else = { 
			set_variable = { 
				name = trade_in_$good$
				value = var:trade_sply_$good$
			}
			set_variable = { 
				name = trade_out_$good$
				value = var:trade_sply_$good$
			}
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = trade_earn_$good$
			value = var:trade_out_$good$
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = trade_pay_$good$
			value = var:trade_in_$good$
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = trade_earn_$good$
			multiply = var:trade_price_$good$
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = trade_pay_$good$
			multiply = var:trade_price_$good$
		}
	}
	else = { 
		set_variable = { 
			name = trade_in_$good$
			value = 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = trade_out_$good$
			value = 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = trade_earn_$good$
			value = 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = trade_pay_$good$
			value = 0
		}
	}
	clear_variable_list = trade_dat_cereal

		value = 0

		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_luxury_food
			var:trade_luxury_food > 0
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = trade_do_trade_t
			add = var:trade_luxury_food
		}
	}

		}

			limit = { 
				OR = { 
					NOT = { 
						has_variable = trade_sply_food

						compare_value < prev.var:trade_do_trade_t
					}
				}
			}

				name = trade_out_food
				value = var:trade_sply_food
			}
		}

	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				OR = { 
					NOT = { 
						has_variable = trade_sply_tools
					}
					var:trade_sply_tools = { 
						compare_value < prev.var:trade_do_trade_t
					}
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				name = trade_out_tools
				value = var:trade_sply_tools
			}
		}
		else = { 
			change_variable = { 
				name = trade_out_tools
				add = var:trade_do_trade_t
			}
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_power_t
		value = var:trade_power
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_power_t
		multiply = 5
	}
}

					subtract = prev.var:trade_price_food
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						has_variable = trade_point_food
						var:trade_point_food < 0
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_point_food
						multiply = -1
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					name = trade_point_food
					multiply = 100
				}
				change_variable = { 
					name = trade_point_food
					add = 1
				}
				change_variable = { 
					name = trade_point_food
					divide = trade_power_cost_food
				}
				change_variable = { 
					name = trade_point_food
					divide = var:trade_cost
				}
			}

						value = var:trade_do_trade_t
					}

						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						multiply = 100
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						divide = prev.var:trade_do_trade_t
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						multiply = prev.var:trade_do_trade_tt
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						divide = 100
					}

						name = trade_do_trade_tt
						add = var:trade_do_trade_ttt
					}
				}

					limit = { 
						var:trade_sell_salt > 0
						var:trade_point_salt > 0
						var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
					}
					variable = trade_do_trade_list
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							has_variable = trade_do_trade_tt
							var:trade_do_trade_tt = { 
								compare_value >= prev.var:trade_sell_salt
							}
						}
						change_variable = { 
							name = trade_do_trade_ttt
							subtract = var:trade_do_trade_tt
						}
						change_variable = { 
							name = trade_do_trade_ttt
							add = var:trade_sell_salt
						}
						set_variable = { 
							name = trade_do_trade_tt
							value = var:trade_sell_salt
						}
						prev = { 
							change_variable = { 
								name = trade_do_trade_t
								subtract = prev.var:trade_do_trade_t
							}
						}

							name = trade_do_trade_t
							value = 0
						}
					}

						}
					}

					limit = { 
						OR = { 
							NOT = { 
								has_variable = trade_do_trade_ttt
							}

						}
					}
					set_variable = {

						value = 0
					}

						name = trade_do_trade_tt
						subtract = var:trade_do_trade_ttt
					}
				}

				set_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_ttt
					value = 0
				}
				every_in_global_list = { 
					limit = { 
						var:trade_sell_tools > 0
						var:trade_point_tools > 0
						var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
					}
					variable = trade_do_trade_list
					set_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						value = var:trade_do_trade_t
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						multiply = 100
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						divide = prev.var:trade_do_trade_t
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						multiply = prev.var:trade_do_trade_tt
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_ttt
						divide = 100
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_tt
						add = var:trade_do_trade_ttt
					}
				}
				every_in_global_list = { 
					limit = { 
						var:trade_sell_tools > 0
						var:trade_point_tools > 0
						var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
					}
					variable = trade_do_trade_list
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							has_variable = trade_do_trade_tt
							var:trade_do_trade_tt = { 
								compare_value >= prev.var:trade_sell_tools
							}
						}
						change_variable = { 
							name = trade_do_trade_ttt
							subtract = var:trade_do_trade_tt
						}
						change_variable = { 
							name = trade_do_trade_ttt
							add = var:trade_sell_tools
						}
						set_variable = { 
							name = trade_do_trade_tt
							value = var:trade_sell_tools
						}
						prev = { 
							change_variable = { 
								name = trade_do_trade_t
								subtract = prev.var:trade_do_trade_t
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							name = trade_do_trade_t
							value = 0
						}
					}
					prev = { 
						change_variable = { 
							name = trade_do_trade_ttt
							add = prev.var:trade_do_trade_ttt
						}
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						OR = { 
							NOT = { 
								has_variable = trade_do_trade_ttt
							}
							var:trade_do_trade_ttt < 0.01
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_tt
						value = 0
					}
				}
				else = { 
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_tt
						subtract = var:trade_do_trade_ttt
					}
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				name = trade_sum_sell_tools
				value = 0
			}

						value = 0
					}
					remove_variable = trade_point_tools

						name = trade_sell_tools
						value = var:trade_do_trade_tt

								value = 0

					}

				if = { 
					limit = {

		}
		every_in_global_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_list
			save_temporary_scope_as = trade_do_trade_select
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					OR = { 
						AND = { 
							has_variable = trade_buy_food
							var:trade_buy_food > 0.1
						}
						AND = { 
							has_variable = trade_sell_food
							var:trade_sell_food > 0.1
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					value = 0
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						has_variable = trade_buy_food
						var:trade_buy_food > 0.1
					}
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						add = var:trade_buy_food
					}
				}
				else = { 
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						subtract = var:trade_sell_food
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						has_variable_list = trade_dat_food
						is_target_in_variable_list = { 
							name = trade_dat_food
							target = prev
						}
					}
					set_global_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						value = 0
					}
					set_global_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_tt
					}
					every_in_list = { 
						limit = { 
							has_global_variable = trade_do_trade_tt
						}
						variable = trade_dat_food
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								has_variable = trade_power
								this = global_var:trade_do_trade_select
							}
							remove_global_variable = trade_do_trade_tt
						}
						else = { 
							change_global_variable = { 
								name = trade_do_trade_t
								add = 1
							}
						}
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_dat_food
						target = prev
					}
					set_global_variable = { 
						name = array_change_t
						value = global_var:trade_do_trade_t
					}
					ordered_in_list = { 
						variable = array_trade_dat_food
						position = global_var:array_change_t
						prev = { 
							set_variable = { 
								name = array_change_t
								value = prev
							}
							change_variable = { 
								name = array_change_t
								divide = 10
							}
							change_variable = { 
								name = array_change_t
								subtract = var:trade_do_trade_t
							}
							remove_list_variable = { 
								name = array_trade_dat_food
								target = prev
							}
							set_variable = { 
								name = array_add_t
								value = var:array_change_t
							}
							change_variable = { 
								name = array_add_t
								multiply = 10
							}
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									NOT = { 
										has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_food
									}
								}
								add_to_variable_list = { 
									name = array_trade_dat_food
									target = var:array_add_t
								}
							}
							else = { 
								while = { 
									limit = { 
										is_target_in_variable_list = { 
											name = array_trade_dat_food
											target = var:array_add_t
										}
									}
									count = 10
									change_variable = { 
										name = array_add_t
										add = 0.001
									}

						add = var:trade_buy_pottery

				}
				else = {

						subtract = var:trade_sell_pottery

							name = trade_dat_pottery
							target = prev

						add = prev.var:trade_sell_tools
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					name = trade_sell_tools
					multiply = var:trade_do_trade_t
				}
				change_variable = { 
					name = trade_earn_tools
					add = var:trade_sell_tools
				}
				prev = { 
					change_variable = { 
						name = trade_pay_tools
						add = prev.var:trade_sell_tools
					}
				}
			}
			remove_variable = trade_do_trade_dist
		}
		remove_global_variable = trade_do_trade_select
		clear_global_variable_list = trade_do_trade_list
		set_variable = { 
			name = trade_power_t
			value = 0
		}
	}
}

	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_cereal
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_cereal
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_cereal
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_cereal
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_cereal
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}

		name = trade_do_trade_t

		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_salted
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_salted
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_salted
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_salted
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}

			variable = trade_do_trade_t

			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_salted
					target = prev.var:trade_location

					target = prev

				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_salt
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = {

	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}

				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t

	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_salt
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_salt
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_salt
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_salt
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t

			variable = trade_do_trade_t

				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_mud
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_mud
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}

			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_mud
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}

			}

		value = global_var:array_get_min_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_min_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_min_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_min_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t < 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_fuel
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fuel
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_fuel
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fuel
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_fuel
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_min_t
		value = 0
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_min_tt
		value = 0
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = array_get_min_t
		value = 210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_min_t = { 
					compare_value > prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_min_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_min_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_min_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_min_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_min_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}

		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_min_tt
	}

			prev = {

					name = trade_dat_fuel

				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_min_t = { 
					compare_value > prev
				}
			}

		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t < 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_fiber
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fiber
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_fiber
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fiber
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_fiber
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = {

						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}

				name = array_trade_dat_metal
				target = var:array_add_t
			}

					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_metal
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}

			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_metal
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

	remove_variable = trade_do_trade_t_exotics_w
	remove_variable = trade_do_trade_tt_exotics_w
	remove_variable = trade_do_trade_ttt_exotics_w
	remove_variable = trade_dat_trade_in_exotics_w
	remove_variable = trade_dat_trade_out_exotics_w
	remove_variable = trade_dat_trade_earn_exotics_w
	remove_variable = trade_dat_trade_pay_exotics_w
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = trade_dat_exotics_e
		prev = { 
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = trade_do_trade_t
				target = prev
			}
		}
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
		prev = { 
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_do_trade_t
				target = prev
			}
		}
	}
	clear_variable_list = trade_dat_exotics_e
	clear_variable_list = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = 0
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_tt
		value = 0
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = -210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_exotics_e
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t

			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

		name = trade_do_trade_t

		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_exotics_g
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_g
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_exotics_g
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_g
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_exotics_g
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

					name = array_add_t

				}

			}

			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_pottery
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = {

				name = array_trade_dat_pottery

			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_pottery

					}
				}

					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}

			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_tools
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_tools
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_tools
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_tools
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				add_to_variable_list = { 
					name = trade_dat_tools
					target = prev.var:trade_location
				}
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_min_t
		value = 0
	}

		name = array_get_min_tt
		value = 0

		name = array_get_min_t

		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t

			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_min_t = { 
					compare_value > prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_min_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_min_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_min_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_min_t
			add = 1
		}
	}

				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_food
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = {

				value = global_var:array_get_max_t

	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_food
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_food
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_food
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_food
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t

			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = {

						target = prev.var:trade_location

					remove_list_variable = {

	remove_global_variable = array_get_min_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_min_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t < 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_food
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_food
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_food
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_food
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_food
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_food
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}

			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t < 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_cereal
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_cereal
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_cereal
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_cereal
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_cereal
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_cereal
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_min_t
		value = 0
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_min_tt
		value = 0
	}

		name = array_get_min_t
		value = 210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_min_t = { 
					compare_value > prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_min_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_min_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_min_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_min_t
			add = 1
		}
	}

		name = trade_do_trade_t

		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_salted
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_salted
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_salted
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_salted
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_salted
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = {

					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_salted
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}

			multiply = 10
		}

		}

				limit = {

					}

					name = array_add_t

				}

				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = 0
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_tt
		value = 0
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = -210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_salt
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_salt
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_salt
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_salt
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_salt
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_salt
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = {

					target = prev

			}

	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_tt
		value = 0
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = -210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_mud
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_mud
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_mud
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_mud
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_mud
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_mud
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}

					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fuel
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_fuel
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_fuel
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = 0
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_tt
		value = 0
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = -210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_fuel
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fuel
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_fuel
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fuel
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value

					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t

				}

					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}

				name = array_get_min_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_min_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_min_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}

			name = array_get_min_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_min_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_min_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_min_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_min_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_min_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t < 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_fuel
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fuel
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_fuel
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_fuel
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_fuel
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_fuel
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_timber
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_timber
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_timber
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_timber
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_timber
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_timber
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_timber
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_timber
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}

			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t

			}

		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_timber
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_timber
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_timber
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_timber
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}

				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_metal
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_metal
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = 0
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_tt
		value = 0
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = -210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_metal
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_metal
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_metal
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_metal
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_metal
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_metal
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

	remove_variable = trade_dat_trade_earn_metal
	remove_variable = trade_dat_trade_pay_metal
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = trade_dat_exotics_w
		prev = { 
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = trade_do_trade_t
				target = prev
			}
		}
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_dat_exotics_w
		prev = { 
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_do_trade_t
				target = prev
			}
		}
	}
	clear_variable_list = trade_dat_exotics_w
	clear_variable_list = array_trade_dat_exotics_w
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = 0
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_tt
		value = 0
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = -210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_exotics_w
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_w
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_exotics_w
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_w
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_exotics_w
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_exotics_w
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
	}

			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_e
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_exotics_e
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_exotics_e
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

				}
				count = 10

					add = 0.001
				}

			}

			if = {

				}

						name = trade_dat_exotics_e

				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}

				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_exotics_g
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_exotics_g
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = {

						name = trade_dat_exotics_g
						target = prev.var:trade_location

			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_textile
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_textile
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_textile
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_textile
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_textile
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_textile
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

					compare_value < prev
				}
			}

				value = global_var:array_get_max_t

					value = prev
				}
			}
		}

			name = array_get_max_t

		}

		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_textile
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_textile
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_textile
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}

				name = array_trade_dat_textile
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}

					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}

		value = 0
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = array_get_max_t
		value = -210000
	}
	every_in_list = { 
		variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				prev.var:array_get_max_t = { 
					compare_value < prev
				}
			}
			set_global_variable = { 
				name = array_get_max_tt
				value = global_var:array_get_max_t
			}
			prev = { 
				set_variable = { 
					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}
		}
		change_global_variable = { 
			name = array_get_max_t
			add = 1
		}
	}
	set_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = var:array_get_max_t
	}
	change_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		divide = 10
	}
	set_global_variable = { 
		name = trade_do_trade_t
		value = global_var:array_get_max_tt
	}
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_t
	remove_global_variable = array_get_max_tt
	remove_variable = array_get_max_t
	if = { 
		limit = { 
			has_variable = trade_do_trade_t
			var:trade_do_trade_t > 0
		}
		set_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			value = var:trade_do_trade_t
		}
		change_variable = { 
			name = array_add_t
			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_pottery
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_pottery
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_pottery
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_pottery
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_pottery
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_pottery
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

			multiply = 10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_variable_list = array_trade_dat_pottery
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_pottery
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_pottery
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_pottery
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_pottery
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_pottery
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}

					compare_value < prev
				}
			}

					name = array_get_max_t
					value = prev
				}
			}

			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_tools
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		else = { 
			while = { 
				limit = { 
					is_target_in_variable_list = { 
						name = array_trade_dat_tools
						target = var:array_add_t
					}
				}
				count = 10
				change_variable = { 
					name = array_add_t
					add = 0.001
				}
			}
			add_to_variable_list = { 
				name = array_trade_dat_tools
				target = var:array_add_t
			}
		}
		remove_variable = array_add_t
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_variable = trade_power
				}
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_tools
						target = prev.var:trade_location
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				prev = { 
					add_to_variable_list = { 
						name = trade_dat_tools
						target = prev
					}
					remove_list_variable = { 
						name = trade_do_trade_t
						target = prev
					}
				}
			}
		}
		ordered_in_list = { 
			variable = array_trade_do_trade_t
			position = global_var:trade_do_trade_t.compare_value
			prev = { 
				remove_list_variable = { 
					name = array_trade_do_trade_t
					target = prev
				}
			}
		}
